    <title>Android EditText 限制输入两位小数</title>
    <link href="http://myurv.github.io/2018/03/19/Android%20EditText%20%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%A4%E4%BD%8D%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0/"/>
    <id>http://myurv.github.io/2018/03/19/Android EditText 限制输入两位小数/</id>
    <published>2018-03-18T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-07T09:38:48.534Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong> Android EditText 限制输入两位小数: </strong> <excerpt in index | 首页摘要></excerpt></p><h1 id="Android-EditText-限制输入两位小数"><a href="#Android-EditText-限制输入两位小数" class="headerlink" title="Android EditText 限制输入两位小数"></a>Android EditText 限制输入两位小数</h1><h2 id="为什么有这个需求"><a href="#为什么有这个需求" class="headerlink" title="为什么有这个需求"></a>为什么有这个需求</h2><p>这个需求其实很正常，就像用户个人信息有标准一样。比如说涉及到金钱的输入，客户端限制位数是肯定的。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="功能分析"><a href="#功能分析" class="headerlink" title="功能分析"></a>功能分析</h2><ol><li>首位输入 . 的时候补全为0.;</li><li>删除 . 后2位数字；</li><li>如果开始为0，第二位不是.，则后续无法输入。</li></ol><h2 id="TextWatcher-方案"><a href="#TextWatcher-方案" class="headerlink" title="TextWatcher 方案"></a>TextWatcher 方案</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public class DataTextWatcher implements TextWatcher &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    private EditText editText;</span><br><span class="line">    private int digits = 2;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    public DataTextWatcher(EditText et) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        editText = et;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    public DataTextWatcher setDigits(int d) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        digits = d;</span><br><span class="line">        return this;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void beforeTextChanged(CharSequence s, int start, int count, int after) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void onTextChanged(CharSequence s, int start, int before, int count) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        //删除“.”后面超过2位后的数据</span><br><span class="line">        if (s.toString().contains(&quot;.&quot;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            if (s.length() - 1 - s.toString().indexOf(&quot;.&quot;) &gt; digits) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                s = s.toString().subSequence(0,</span><br><span class="line">                        s.toString().indexOf(&quot;.&quot;) + digits+1);</span><br><span class="line">                editText.setText(s);</span><br><span class="line">                editText.setSelection(s.length()); //光标移到最后</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        //如果&quot;.&quot;在起始位置,则起始位置自动补0</span><br><span class="line">        if (s.toString().trim().substring(0).equals(&quot;.&quot;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            s = &quot;0&quot; + s;</span><br><span class="line">            editText.setText(s);</span><br><span class="line">            editText.setSelection(2);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        //如果起始位置为0,且第二位跟的不是&quot;.&quot;,则无法后续输入</span><br><span class="line">        if (s.toString().startsWith(&quot;0&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">                &amp;&amp; s.toString().trim().length() &gt; 1) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            if (!s.toString().substring(1, 2).equals(&quot;.&quot;)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                editText.setText(s.subSequence(0, 1));</span><br><span class="line">                editText.setSelection(1);</span><br><span class="line">                return;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void afterTextChanged(Editable s) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注释很明了了，一看就懂，使用方法也很简单</p>]]></content>
    
