    <title>Android TextView设置字数限制</title>
    <link href="http://myurv.github.io/2018/03/12/Android%20TextView%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%AD%97%E6%95%B0%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/"/>
    <id>http://myurv.github.io/2018/03/12/Android TextView设置字数限制/</id>
    <published>2018-03-11T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-07T08:16:12.597Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>TextView可以设置最大显示字数，其余以省略号显示</p><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;TextView</span><br><span class="line">    android:layout_width=&quot;wrap_content&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:layout_height=&quot;wrap_content&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:text=&quot;哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:singleLine=&quot;true&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:maxEms=&quot;4&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:ellipsize=&quot;end&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:textSize=&quot;14px&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:textColor=&quot;@color/colorText&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    /&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>主要是设置三个属性：</code></pre><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">android:singleLine=&quot;true&quot; //已经过时</span><br><span class="line">android:maxLines=&quot;1&quot; </span><br><span class="line">android:maxEms=&quot;8&quot; //最大字符数</span><br><span class="line">android:ellipsize=&quot;end&quot; //省略号显示位置</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>android:ellipsize=”start”—–省略号显示在开头 &quot;...pedia&quot;android:ellipsize=”end”——省略号显示在结尾  &quot;encyc...&quot;android:ellipsize=”middle”—-省略号显示在中间 &quot;en...dia&quot;android:ellipsize=”marquee”–以横向滚动方式显示(需获得当前焦点时)</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;TextView可以设置最大显示字数，其余以省略号显示&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
